“Software” means TeamsPlus, including binaries/JARs, source code, configuration templates, GUIs, assets, documentation,
and any accompanying materials.
“Source Code” means human-readable code (Java, build files, resources) and any non-obfuscated distribution.
“Protected Build” means an obfuscated/protected compiled distribution of the Software.

